<p>

An update for Day of Defeat has just been released. This release contains two updated maps and several bug fixes. Here's a list of exactly what's included:<br/><br/><ul style="padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><li>Updated dod_escape</li><br/><li>Updated dod_flugplatz</li><br/><li>Fixed linux server</li><br/><li>Fixed mp_clan_restartround - enter 'mp_clan_restartround 1' while in clan mode to restart</li><br/><li>Added mp_clan_readyrestart - enter 'mp_clan_readyrestart 1' - when someone from each team has said 'ready', the round will restart</li><br/><li>Fixed cl_lw recoil exploit</li><br/><li>Minor work to lessen server cpu usage in AddToFullPack</li><br/><li>Fixed speed bug with zooming, sprint and stamina</li><br/><li>Ducking in mid air no longer recovers stamina</li><br/><li>Don't force any help messages if the user has '_ah 0'</li><br/><li>Slowed sniper zoom speed from 70 to 42</li><br/></ul><br/></p>
